            Agent Benchmarks
          </h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-6">
            Understand how different agent architectures are evaluated. We cover industry-standard benchmarks including:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
                <strong>SWE-bench</strong> - Software engineering task completion
              </span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
